      "para_id": "Q001945.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Išme-Dagan , provider of Nibru , steadfast supporter of Urim , tireless servant of Eridug , en priest of Unug , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the beloved spouse of Inana ."
    }
